ition government collapsed due to disagreements over Ukrainian drone incidents. The Progressive Party withdrew support after Silina dismissed the defense minister for failing to address drones flying from Russia. President Edgars Rinkevics will now consult parties to form a new government ahead of October elections.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/latvian-pm-resigns-due-to-split-in-alliance-over-russian-drones/articleshow/131099848.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/latvian-pm-resigns-due-to-split-in-alliance-over-russian-drones/articleshow/131099848.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-14T23:06:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131099964,imgsize-18454.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kick streamer Clavicular’s jaw hammering confession takes unexpected turn after revealing life with multiple girlfriends]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131099846.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Internet personality Clavicular went viral after admitting he used a hammer on his jaw as a teenager to improve his appearance. He said his parents even hid hammers to stop him. The interview also focused on his current dating life, where he claimed to be seeing multiple women at the same time. The clip quickly spread online and sparked heavy discussion.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-claviculars-jaw-hammering-confession-takes-unexpected-turn-after-revealing-life-with-multiple-girlfriends/articleshow/131099846.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-claviculars-jaw-hammering-confession-takes-unexpected-turn-after-revealing-life-with-multiple-girlfriend